        "timestamp": "2020-06-23 13:29:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi,\n\nThis is the last commit of a series which intent to decouple the writing and the formatting logic of the report file generation. It eases testing, opens the door for creating new ways to output the written data (in the console, in a file, in memory, ...) and overall makes the code easier to reason about.\n\nThere will be one last commit to make some minor clean-ups in the code. Once it's done, we will be able to close SDC-2499.\n\nThank you in advance for your help,\n\nFrancis.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
